**Install**

Copy arc-ardour.colors in ~/.config/ardour7/themes/

Copy Ardour-*splash.png in ~/.config/ardour7/resourcess/

Select "arc" in Settings > Colors > Color scheme.
I recommend enabling flat and square buttons options.
Restart ardour after selecting the color scheme.

**Modify**

Edit arc-ardour.colors.in & arc-ardour.py, and run python3 arc-ardour.py
